#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:2 ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:23
msgid "XXE"
msgstr "XXE"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:5
msgid "XML基础"
msgstr "XML Basics"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:6
msgid ""
"XML 指可扩展标记语言（eXtensible Markup "
"Language），是一种用于标记电子文件使其具有结构性的标记语言，被设计用来传输和存储数据。XML文档结构包括XML声明、DTD文档类型定义（可选）、文档元素。目前，XML文件作为配置文件（Spring、Struts2等）、文档结构说明文件（PDF、RSS等）、图片格式文件（SVG"
" header）应用比较广泛。 XML 的语法规范由 DTD （Document Type Definition）来进行控制。"
msgstr ""
"XML stands for eXtensible Markup Language. It is a markup language used to "
"mark electronic documents with structure and is designed to transmit and "
"store data. An XML document structure includes an XML declaration, an "
"optional DTD document type definition, and document elements. XML files are "
"widely used as configuration files such as Spring and Struts2, document "
"structure description files such as PDF and RSS, and image format files such"
" as SVG headers. XML syntax rules are controlled by DTD (Document Type "
"Definition)."

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:9
msgid "基本语法"
msgstr "Basic Syntax"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:10
msgid ""
"XML 文档在开头有 ``<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"yes\"?>``"
" 的结构，这种结构被称为 XML prolog ，用于声明XML文档的版本和编码，是可选的，但是必须放在文档开头。"
msgstr ""
"An XML document may begin with a structure such as ``<?xml version=\"1.0\" "
"encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"yes\"?>``. This structure is called the XML "
"prolog. It declares the XML document version and encoding. It is optional, "
"but if present it must appear at the beginning of the document."

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:12
msgid "除了可选的开头外，XML 语法主要有以下的特性："
msgstr ""
"Apart from the optional prolog, XML syntax mainly has the following "
"characteristics:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:14
msgid "所有 XML 元素都须有关闭标签"
msgstr "All XML elements must have closing tags"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:15
msgid "XML 标签对大小写敏感"
msgstr "XML tags are case-sensitive"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:16
msgid "XML 必须正确地嵌套"
msgstr "XML must be properly nested"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:17
msgid "XML 文档必须有根元素"
msgstr "XML documents must have a root element"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:18
msgid "XML 的属性值需要加引号"
msgstr "XML attribute values must be quoted"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:20
msgid "另外，XML也有CDATA语法，用于处理有多个字符需要转义的情况。"
msgstr ""
"XML also has CDATA syntax for handling cases where multiple characters need "
"to be escaped."

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:24
msgid ""
"当允许引用外部实体时，可通过构造恶意的XML内容，导致读取任意文件、执行系统命令、探测内网端口、攻击内网网站等后果。一般的XXE攻击，只有在服务器有回显或者报错的基础上才能使用XXE漏洞来读取服务器端文件，但是也可以通过Blind"
" XXE的方式实现攻击。"
msgstr ""
"When external entity references are allowed, malicious XML content can cause"
" arbitrary file reads, system command execution, internal port probing, "
"attacks against internal websites, and similar impact. Typical XXE attacks "
"can read server-side files only when the server returns output or errors, "
"but attacks can also be performed through Blind XXE."

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:27
msgid "攻击方式"
msgstr "Attack Methods"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:30
msgid "拒绝服务攻击"
msgstr "Denial-of-Service Attack"

#: ../../source/vuln/xxe.rst:41
msgid "若解析过程非常缓慢，则表示测试成功，目标站点可能有拒绝服务漏洞。 具体攻击可使用更多层的迭代或递归，也可引用巨大的外部实体，以实现攻击的效果。"
msgstr ""
"If parsing becomes very slow, the test is successful and the target site may"
" have a denial-of-service vulnerability. A concrete attack can use more "
"levels of iteration or recursion, or reference huge external entities, to "
"achieve the effect."

